phrases: We were all invited to Shima-chan's holiday home.
It is a bit far from the beach,
but that is what makes it so quiet.
It is really okay for me to have a room with such a great view all to myself?
We have got plenty of rooms left over.
How about we get ready and head for the beach?
How come we are all in the same room?!
It was nice of her to give us a room.
and I get to spend my nights under the same roof as the girl I like.
This is my big chance to get even closer to her
after closing the gap during our Puri Puri Moon event!
But I cannot steal that chance with you guys around!
Well, I think that is exactly why we are all in the same room.
and honestly, I am not even the outdoors type.
I am not a fan of the ocean.
I would rather stay home in the summer!
Maybe I should not have come.
You have been in there a while.
I-I am okay, no need to worry.
Well, that is good to hear.
As I said, that was not it!
Same here, it is been a while.
Should we bet on who is best?
I-I have never done it before.
Looks like we are both beginners.
I have never done it, either.
Th-Then, since we are both beginners
Damn her and her unfair advantages!
W-Well, I am sure we will get the hang of it in no time.
We have just got to keep the right posture, and...
Shinomiya-kun, there is seaweed on your head.
Maybe it was a good thing that I could not do it.
This is no time for seaweed!
Do not tell me he is going to try and surf?
You cannot do it without practice!
I am going to show her how cool I can be.
I am terribly sorry about what happened.
It was not on purpose, so just forget about it.
Cheer up and have some lunch.
If Serinuma-san's forgiven him, then nothing needs to be said.
And then we can all play beach volleyball together.
Senpai, how about we go and borrow a ball?
We can walk off the food.
But Shinomiya-kun's not done eating yet.
Oh, do not worry about him.
We will go on ahead, then.
Check out the ass on that girl with the hoodie.
I really could not care less what you guys have to talk about,
but you better not make a pass at those girls.
All right, let us split into teams.
Well, I do not think they will pull anything funny now.
Actually, that is the first time I have ever seen you angry, Mutsumi-san.
I hate that kind of thing.
Is that why she went on ahead with Serinuma-senpai?
That means I am the only one who did not get it.
What can I do against them?
Are you really happy with this?
I could have had the head cook take care of all this prep work.
A barbecue's better when we do all the work ourselves.
I think I am just a little tired.
No, I have got to get a hold of myself.
I am going to become a reliable guy in my own way.
A guy that can protect Serinuma-senpai.
A guy that can protect her.
We will have to start over?
I should not have come after all.
I am not the outdoors type.
I am not a fan of the ocean.
I would rather stay home in the summer,
and I would have been better off if I had.
If I had just done that,
I would not have to feel this miserable.
He was going home, or something?
Then, why did he run that way?
Is not that just a forest, though?
I kind of had a hunch...
We have got to go after him!
He will come back on his own eventually.
But, it could be dangerous if he stays out until it is dark.
There is no one at the top of this mountain.
It will be dangerous for her alone.
We have to hurry up and find him soon!
Come on, hurry and move already.
There is only one path, so he must have.
The drop was shorter than we thought.
The bridge felt like a bigger deal...
But this might be too high to climb.
There is a path over there.
It should lead to where there used to be an old hotel.
Gosh, she runs off without a thought.
How far could he have gone?
I should have caught up by now...
P-Please do not look at me.
I will free you right away.
How did you end up like that?
The vine got caught around my ankle.
And when I tried to get it off...
For some reason, my hands also got tangled up.
And when I thrashed around to break free...
My entire body got tangled up.
I-I am just happy you are not hurt.
I ended up looking weird in front of her again.
Everyone else is looking for you, too.
We decided to group up ahead here.
But it will be more dangerous if we stay out here!
Let us take shelter from the rain for now.
I wonder if everyone else is okay.
Is not it my fault we ended up here in the first place?
It is because I cannot do anything right, and just get in the way.
I already have experience from sending my lord to the other side!
But that was an illusion caused by mushrooms!
Because I pray for Shion every day!
You are making me even more scared, so stop!
I know you are not good at handling scary things.
But I am fine, so no need to worry.
Forget about not being able to do anything, or not being good enough.
This is no time to lose my nerve.
We wanted to thank you for what happened earlier.
Did you guys have fun at the haunted house?
Those are the guys from the beach house.
We came to see who was crashing our hangout, and it is you guys!
Plus, those troublemakers with you before are not here.
And did you just say, I will protect you to her?
When you were the brat that just hid behind those other guys?
we would kill you if you made a pass at her?
So, that detour we took was crazy.
There were snakes, and I swear there was a wild boar, too.
I thought we were done for.
And Nishina, next time tell us if there is a connected public road on the other side.
I really did not know about it, though.
I am sorry that I caused so much trouble.
We are all used to your freak-outs already.
I am not strong like these guys are.
And maybe I am not on the same level as them yet,
I do not want to lose her to anyone.
I feel so bored and lifeless.
I am sure he just has not bothered finishing his summer homework.
I know you are cheating with the other soccer club guys.
Sure, but a trade's got to be fair.
What are you going to do for me?
You can do it all in just two days!
I used to think it was impossible, too.
